column25:
long-description:"※The items offered in this pack can be purchased as a single item. Refunds will not be offered for duplicate purchase.

PRE-ORDER OFFER:
Pre-order now and get 3-days early access to the The Crew® 2 Legendary Motors Pack* including the following vehicles:
+ MERCEDES-AMG C 63 Touring Car 2016
+ HARLEY-DAVIDSON IRON 883TM 2017

The Crew 2 - Digital Gold Edition includes:
+ The Crew 2 Basegame
+ Motorsports Deluxe Pack
+ Season Pass

Motorsports Deluxe Pack includes:
+ PILATUS PC-21
+ ABARTH 500 2008 MONSTER TRUCK EDITION
+ FORD F-150 RAPTOR RACE TRUCK 2017
+ FREESTYLE outfit
+ MONSTER RALLY outfit
+ RALLY RAID outfit

Copyright:
© 2017 Ubisoft Entertainment. All Rights Reserved. Far Cry

Purchase or use of this item is subject to SEN Terms of Service and User Agreement."
